contentrichtext.text: '''Hing''' is another name for the spice [[asafoetida]] derived from the plant ''Ferula assa-foetida'' '''Hing''' may also refer to: * [[Hing Tong]] (1922-2007), American mathematician * [[Kwan Tak Hing]] (1905-1996), Hong Kong actor * [[Kwong Siu Hing]] (born 1929), Chinese billionaire * [[Lai Yee Hing]] (21st century), Singaporean organic chemistry professor * [[Leung Hing Kit]] (born 1989), Hong Kong professional football player * [[Lew Hing]] (1858-1934), American businessman * [[Ng Moon Hing]] (born 1955), Anglican bishop * [[Hing (surname)]] * Hing means "soul, life, ghost, spirit, breath" in the [[Estonian language]] ==See also== * [[Cheung-Hing]] {{wiktionary|hing}} {{disambig}}
